pickupLocation.name: Stockholm Söder Skanstull/Self Service Kiosk
pickupLocation.infoTextLocationEnglish: You'll find the Self Service Kiosk via the main entrance of Ringvägen 100. Outside office hours you need a pin code to enter the parking garage. Please enter 1727 for april or 2899 for may on the box that belongs to Aimo Park. Follow the Aimo Park signs straight ahead to the courtyard, use entry F to the left. After approximately 10 metres you'll be located on level 4. Take the stairs or elevator down to level 3. The Self Service Kiosk is located at the entrance to the parking lot.
pickupLocation.infoTextLocationNative: Du hittar självservicekiosken via huvudentren på Ringvägen 100. Följ Aimo Park skyltarna rakt fram till innergården, ta ingång F, snett till vänster. pickupLocation.infoTextParkingEnglish: The cars are parked at level 3, the same level as the self service kiosk.
pickupLocation.infoTextParkingNative: Bilarna står parkerade på plan 3, samma plan som självservicekiosken.
pickupLocation.infoTextMiscEnglish: To exit onto Ringvägen 100 outside office hours, enter the code on the device belonging to Aimo Park – June: Code 8334, July: Code 2197. Please note that the garage closes at 11:00 PM.
pickupLocation.infoTextMiscNative: För att komma ut på Ringvägen 100 utanför kontorstid, ange kod på dosan som tillhör Aimo Park - Juni: Kod 8334, Juli: Kod 2197. Observera att garaget stänger kl.23.00.
pickupLocation.infoTextReturnEnglish: Enter Aimo Park P-hus Skanstull via Skansbrogatan and follow the signs to level 3. Park the car in a designated Hertz space on level 3. Leave the key at the kiosk or in the key drop box to the right of the entrance door to the Hertz office on level 3.
pickupLocation.infoTextReturnNative: Kör in i Aimo Park P-hus Skanstull via Skansbrogatan och följ skyltarna till plan 3. Parkera bilen på en märkt Hertz plats på plan 3. Lämna nyckeln i kiosken alternativt i nyckelinkastet till höger om entrédörren till Hertz kontoret på plan3.
